# vDSP_biquad_DestroySetupD

**Function**

Destroys a double-precision biquadratic filter setup object.

## Declaration

```swift
extern void vDSP_biquad_DestroySetupD(vDSP_biquad_SetupD __setup);
```

## Parameters

- **__setup**: The object to be destroyed; a setup created by [doc://com.apple.accelerate/documentation/Accelerate/vDSP_biquad_CreateSetupD].

## Discussion

This function is the same as [doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/kernel/1579970-vdsp_biquadm_destroysetup], except for the type of the `setup` parameter.

## Destroying a single-channel biquadratic filter setup

- **vDSP_biquad_DestroySetup**: Destroys a single-precision biquadratic filter setup object.
